title: I Don't Believe It
lyrics:
Deserve the rush
That lingers long enough
You do no harm
But this suddenness
Sweeps in
Catches my breath



"nothing's the same as anything else"



I can't confess

At least not yet

Inconsolable mess



Time to make eyes

Longing aches fade in time

And echoes do no harm

Tenses combine

Odds slip

You fuzz the signs



"nothing's the same as anything else"



You don't expect

At least not yet

Illegible death



"nothing's meant to be"
